ANIMATED.name: Animated
ANIMATED.description: Your team members takes one third less damage from sources that aren't attacks.

ARTILLERY.name: Artillery
ARTILLERY.description: Your team members deal 20% more move damage after their first turn.

ASSASSIN.name: Assassin
ASSASSIN.description: Your team deals 20% more move damage on their first turn out.

BUSHWHACKER.name: Bushwhacker
BUSHWHACKER.description: Your team's 'Not Very Effective' or 'Barely Effective' moves deal 50% more damage.

CARETAKER.name: Caretaker
CARETAKER.description: Your team members heal for 1/10th HP when swapping out. Your Aid Kit heals for 25% more.

CHARMER.name: Charmer
CHARMER.description: Your team takes 20% less move damage on the turns they enter.

DECEIVER.name: Deceiver
DECEIVER.description: Enemy trainers majorly overestimate how much damage their moves do.

FORTUNE.name: Fortune
FORTUNE.description: Your moves have a +30% chance to activate their moves' additional effects.

HARMONIC.name: Harmonic
HARMONIC.description: Your team take 10% less move damage.

INDUSTRIOUS.name: Industrious
INDUSTRIOUS.description: You gain 10% more money from battles. If you have more than $100,000, your team gets a boost to Attack, Defense, Sp. Atk, and Sp. Def (before modifiers). This bonus scales with the level cap.

LOYAL.name: Loyal
LOYAL.description: Your team members gain 10% more EXP in battles. They also get a small boost to Attack, Defense, Sp. Atk, and Sp. Def (before modifiers). This bonus scales with the level cap.

MYSTIC.name: Mystic
MYSTIC.description: Whenever a member of your team uses a status move, they'll deal 25% more move damage next turn.

NOBLE.name: Noble
NOBLE.description: Your team members take 15% less move damage if they're using a status move this turn.

RADIANT.name: Radiant
RADIANT.description: Your team has 30% increased Sp. Def. Foes can't lower your team's Sp. Def.

SCAVENGER.name: Scavenger
SCAVENGER.description: Your team members berries heal them for 25% more (multiplicative) and their gem-boosted attacks deal 25% more damage (multiplicative).

SCOURGE.name: Scourge
SCOURGE.description: Your able party members and battlers heal for 1/10th HP whenever a foe faints.

SCRAPPER.name: Scrapper
SCRAPPER.description: Your team has 30% increased Defense. Foes can't lower your team's Defense.

SERENE.name: Serene
SERENE.description: Enemy Pokemon's chance to activate their additional effects against your team members is halved.

TACTICIAN.name: Tactician
TACTICIAN.description: Your Pokemon deal 15% more damage to targets that haven’t moved yet this turn. Your priority attacks and priority status moves have doubled PP.

TYRANNICAL.name: Tyrannical
TYRANNICAL.description: Ignore the first time each battle that one of your team members would flinch or get a status condition.

WARRIOR.name: Warrior
WARRIOR.description: Your team members take 15% less move damage if they're using an attack this turn.

ADAPTED.name: Adapted
ADAPTED.description: Powers up moves of the same type by 33%.

ANALYTIC.name: Analytic
ANALYTIC.description: Boosts move power when the Pokémon moves last by 30%.

ASONEGHOST.name: As One
ASONEGHOST.description: Possesses two Abilities: Unnerve and Grim Neigh.

ASONEICE.name: As One
ASONEICE.description: Possesses two Abilities: Unnerve and Chilling Neigh.

AURABREAK.name: Aura Break
AURABREAK.description: Reverses "Aura" Abilities to weaken affected moves.

BADDREAMS.name: Bad Dreams
BADDREAMS.description: Reduces a sleeping foe's HP by 1/8th at the end of a round.

BATTERY.name: Battery
BATTERY.description: Powers up ally Pokémon's special moves by 30%.

BERSERK.name: Berserk
BERSERK.description: Raises Attack and Sp. Atk by two steps when its HP is lowered below half.

CHEEKPOUCH.name: Cheek Pouch
CHEEKPOUCH.description: When the Pokémon eats a Berry, it restores 33% of its max health.

CHILLINGNEIGH.name: Chilling Neigh
CHILLINGNEIGH.description: Boosts Attack after knocking out any Pokémon.

CHLOROPHYLL.name: Chlorophyll
CHLOROPHYLL.description: Doubles the Pokémon's Speed in sunshine.

CLEARBODY.name: Clear Body
CLEARBODY.description: Prevents stat steps from being lowered (except when self-inflicted).

COMATOSE.name: Comatose
COMATOSE.description: It's always drowsing, and attacks without waking.

COMPETITIVE.name: Competitive
COMPETITIVE.description: Raises Sp. Atk by four steps when a stat is lowered by a foe.

CONTRARY.name: Contrary
CONTRARY.description: Makes stat changes have an opposite effect.

CORROSION.name: Corrosion
CORROSION.description: Can poison the target even if it's a Steel or Poison-type.

COTTONDOWN.name: Cotton Down
COTTONDOWN.description: Lowers everyone else's Speed by two steps when hit by an attack.

CUDCHEW.name: Cud Chew
CUDCHEW.description: When the Pokémon eats a Berry, it will regurgitate that Berry at the end of the next turn and eat it one more time.

CURIOUSMEDICINE.name: Curious Medicine
CURIOUSMEDICINE.description: Upon entry, clears the stat changes of other Pokémon.

DANCER.name: Dancer
DANCER.description: Repeats another Pokémon's dance move immediately.

DARKAURA.name: Dark Aura
DARKAURA.description: Powers up each Pokémon's Dark-type moves.

DAUNTLESSSHIELD.name: Dauntless Shield
DAUNTLESSSHIELD.description: Raises Defense when the Pokémon enters a battle.

DEFEATIST.name: Defeatist
DEFEATIST.description: Halves move damage when HP becomes half or less.

DEFIANT.name: Defiant
DEFIANT.description: Raises Attack by four steps when a stat is lowered by a foe.

DELTASTREAM.name: Delta Stream
DELTASTREAM.description: Changes the weather to Strong Winds, which remove Flying-type's weaknesses. Lingers for 3 turns after leaving.

DESOLATELAND.name: Desolate Land
DESOLATELAND.description: Changes the weather to Harsh Sunlight, which nullifies Water-type moves. Lingers for 3 turns after leaving.

DISGUISE.name: Disguise
DISGUISE.description: Its shroud protects it from an attack just once.

DOWNLOAD.name: Download
DOWNLOAD.description: Boosts either Attack or Sp. Atk by two steps according to the foe's defenses.

DRIZZLE.name: Drizzle
DRIZZLE.description: Summons rainstorm for 4 turns when it enters battle.

DROUGHT.name: Drought
DROUGHT.description: Turns the weather to sunshine for 4 turns when it enters battle.

DRYSKIN.name: Dry Skin
DRYSKIN.description: Heals 1/8 HP in rainstorm, 1/4 when hit by Water-type moves. Loses 1/8 in sunshine, takes 25% more from Fire-type moves.

EMERGENCYEXIT.name: Emergency Exit
EMERGENCYEXIT.description: Switches out if its HP becomes half or less.

FAIRYAURA.name: Fairy Aura
FAIRYAURA.description: Powers up each Pokémon's Fairy-type moves.

FILTER.name: Filter
FILTER.description: Reduces damage from super-effective attacks by 25%.

FLAMEBODY.name: Flame Body
FLAMEBODY.description: Physical moves against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to burn the attacker.

FLOWERGIFT.name: Flower Gift
FLOWERGIFT.description: In sunshine boosts its and allies' Attack and Sp. Def by 50%.

FLOWERVEIL.name: Flower Veil
FLOWERVEIL.description: Protects Grass-type allies from non-volatile status conditions or stat reductions (except self-inflicted).

FLUFFY.name: Fluffy
FLUFFY.description: Doubles Defense. The Pokémon takes double damage from Fire-type moves.

FRIENDGUARD.name: Friend Guard
FRIENDGUARD.description: Reduces damage done to allies by 25%.

FULLMETALBODY.name: Full Metal Body
FULLMETALBODY.description: Prevents stat steps from being lowered (except when self-inflicted).

GALEWINGS.name: Gale Wings
GALEWINGS.description: The user's Speed is doubled while using Flying-type moves.

GALVANIZE.name: Galvanize
GALVANIZE.description: Normal-type moves become Electric-type and power up by 30%.

GLUTTONY.name: Gluttony
GLUTTONY.description: Will eat berries normally eaten at 25% HP (in a pinch) at 50% instead.

GOOEY.name: Gooey
GOOEY.description: Physical moves against it lower the attacker's Speed and Attack.

GORILLATACTICS.name: Gorilla Tactics
GORILLATACTICS.description: Boosts Attack by 50% but the user is locked into the first move they use.

GRIMNEIGH.name: Grim Neigh
GRIMNEIGH.description: Boosts Sp. Atk after knocking out any Pokémon.

GULPMISSILE.name: Gulp Missile
GULPMISSILE.description: Attacks with prey caught when using Surf, Dive, or Depth Charge.

HUNGERSWITCH.name: Hunger Switch
HUNGERSWITCH.description: It alternates between an Electric-type Mode and a Dark-type Mode.

HUSTLE.name: Hustle
HUSTLE.description: Boosts move damage by 50%, but lowers Accuracy by 20%.

HYDRATION.name: Hydration
HYDRATION.description: Heals non-volatile status conditions each turn if in rainstorm.

ICEBODY.name: Ice Body
ICEBODY.description: Heals 1/8th of its max HP each turn in a hail.

ILLUSION.name: Illusion
ILLUSION.description: Comes out disguised as the Pokémon in back.

IMPOSTER.name: Imposter
IMPOSTER.description: It transforms itself into the Pokémon it is facing.

INFILTRATOR.name: Infiltrator
INFILTRATOR.description: Ignores screens and other barriers, Substitute, and boosted Defense and Sp. Def.

INNARDSOUT.name: Innards Out
INNARDSOUT.description: Damages an attacker that lands the finishing hit.

INNERFOCUS.name: Inner Focus
INNERFOCUS.description: The Pokémon is protected from flinching, Intimidate, Fascinate, and Frustrate.

INTIMIDATE.name: Intimidate
INTIMIDATE.description: Upon entry, lowers the foe's Attack stat by two steps.

INTREPIDSWORD.name: Intrepid Sword
INTREPIDSWORD.description: Raises Attack when the Pokémon enters a battle.

IRONBARBS.name: Iron Barbs
IRONBARBS.description: Physical moves against it inflict 1/8th max HP damage to the foe.

IRONFIST.name: Iron Fist
IRONFIST.description: Boosts the power of punching moves by 30%.

LEAFGUARD.name: Leaf Guard
LEAFGUARD.description: Immune to non-volatile status conditions while in sunshine.

LEVITATE.name: Levitate
LEVITATE.description: Immune to Ground-type moves. Immune to grounded hazards.

MAGICBOUNCE.name: Magic Bounce
MAGICBOUNCE.description: Reflects enemy status moves that target the Pokémon or create hazards around it.

MAGICGUARD.name: Magic Guard
MAGICGUARD.description: The Pokémon only takes damage from attacks.

MAGICIAN.name: Magician
MAGICIAN.description: Steals the held item of a Pokémon it hits.

MEGALAUNCHER.name: Mega Launcher
MEGALAUNCHER.description: Boosts the power of pulse moves by 50%.

MERCILESS.name: Merciless
MERCILESS.description: Its attacks are critical against poisoned targets.

MOTORDRIVE.name: Motor Drive
MOTORDRIVE.description: Grants immunity to Electric-type moves and boosts Speed when hit by one.

MOXIE.name: Moxie
MOXIE.description: Raises Attack after knocking out any Pokémon.

MULTISCALE.name: Multiscale
MULTISCALE.description: Reduces move damage taken by 50% when HP is full.

MULTITYPE.name: Multitype
MULTITYPE.description: Changes type to match the held Plate.

MUMMY.name: Mummy
MUMMY.description: When the Pokémon is hit by an attack, the attacker's ability becomes Mummy.

NATURALCURE.name: Natural Cure
NATURALCURE.description: All non-volatile status conditions heal when it switches out.

NEUTRALIZINGGAS.name: Neutralizing Gas
NEUTRALIZINGGAS.description: Abilities will be nullified or will not be triggered.

NOGUARD.name: No Guard
NOGUARD.description: Attacks by or against the Pokémon can't miss.

NORMALIZE.name: Normalize
NORMALIZE.description: Non-Normal moves become Normal-type and are powered up by 50%.

PARENTALBOND.name: Parental Bond
PARENTALBOND.description: Child attacks after the parent, for 25% of the previous damage.

PERISHBODY.name: Perish Body
PERISHBODY.description: When it takes a hit, the Pokémon and the attacker both faint after 3 turns.

POISONPOINT.name: Poison Point
POISONPOINT.description: Physical attacks against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to poison the attacker.

POISONTOUCH.name: Poison Touch
POISONTOUCH.description: Physical moves have a 30% chance to poison targets.

POWERCONSTRUCT.name: Power Construct
POWERCONSTRUCT.description: Changes with other Cells if HP becomes half or less.

POWEROFALCHEMY.name: Power of Alchemy
POWEROFALCHEMY.description: When an ally faints, the Pokémon also gains their ability or abilities.

POWERSPOT.name: Power Spot
POWERSPOT.description: Powers up nearby allies moves by 30%.

PRANKSTER.name: Prankster
PRANKSTER.description: Gives priority to status moves, but makes Dark-types immune to them.

PRESSURE.name: Pressure
PRESSURE.description: The Pokémon raises the foe's PP usage.

PRIMORDIALSEA.name: Primordial Sea
PRIMORDIALSEA.description: Changes the weather to Heavy Rain, which nullifies Fire-type moves. Lingers for 3 turns after leaving.

PRISMARMOR.name: Prism Armor
PRISMARMOR.description: The Pokémon receives 25% less move damage from super-effective attacks.

PROTEAN.name: Protean
PROTEAN.description: It changes type to that of the move it's about to use.

PUREFORCE.name: Pure Force
PUREFORCE.description: Raises the Pokémon's Attack by 50%, including Style Values and other bonuses.

RAINDISH.name: Rain Dish
RAINDISH.description: Heals 1/8th of its max HP each turn if in rainstorm.

RECKLESS.name: Reckless
RECKLESS.description: Powers up moves that have recoil damage by 30%.

REGENERATOR.name: Regenerator
REGENERATOR.description: Restores 25% of max HP when withdrawn from battle.

RIPEN.name: Ripen
RIPEN.description: Ripens Berries and doubles their effect.

RKSSYSTEM.name: RKS System
RKSSYSTEM.description: Its type matches the memory disc it holds.

ROCKHEAD.name: Rock Head
ROCKHEAD.description: Protects the Pokémon from recoil damage.

ROUGHSKIN.name: Rough Skin
ROUGHSKIN.description: Physical moves against it inflict 1/8th max HP damage to the foe.

SANDRUSH.name: Sand Rush
SANDRUSH.description: Doubles the Pokémon's Speed in a sandstorm.

SANDSHROUD.name: Sand Shroud
SANDSHROUD.description: Takes 30% less damage in a sandstorm.

SANDSTREAM.name: Sand Stream
SANDSTREAM.description: Summons a sandstorm for 4 turns when it enters battle.

SAPSIPPER.name: Sap Sipper
SAPSIPPER.description: Immune to Grass-type moves, and raises Attack and Sp. Atk when hit by one.

SCHOOLING.name: Schooling
SCHOOLING.description: Forms a powerful school while it has a lot of HP.

SERENEGRACE.name: Serene Grace
SERENEGRACE.description: Doubles the likelihood of the user's random added effects activating.

SHADOWSHIELD.name: Shadow Shield
SHADOWSHIELD.description: Resists damage while its HP is full.

SHEDSKIN.name: Shed Skin
SHEDSKIN.description: At the end of each turn, heals from every non-volatile status condition (except Sleep).

SHEERFORCE.name: Sheer Force
SHEERFORCE.description: Removes random added effects of attacks to increase their damage by 30%.

SHIELDDUST.name: Shield Dust
SHIELDDUST.description: Blocks all random added effects of attacks taken.

SHIELDSDOWN.name: Shields Down
SHIELDSDOWN.description: Immune to non-volatile status conditions while it has its shell. Below half HP, its shell breaks and it turns aggressive.

SIMPLE.name: Simple
SIMPLE.description: Stat changes in the Pokémon are doubled.

SKILLLINK.name: Skill Link
SKILLLINK.description: Maximizes the frequency of multi-strike moves.

SLOWSTART.name: Slow Start
SLOWSTART.description: Halves Attack and Speed for 3 turns.

SLUSHRUSH.name: Slush Rush
SLUSHRUSH.description: Doubles the Pokémon's Speed stat in a hail.

SNIPER.name: Sniper
SNIPER.description: Doubles the critical hit chance of random crit moves. Powers up critical hits by another 50%.

SNOWWARNING.name: Snow Warning
SNOWWARNING.description: Summons a hail for 4 turns when it enters battle.

SOLARPOWER.name: Solar Power
SOLARPOWER.description: In sunshine, Sp. Atk is boosted by 50%, but the Pokémon is hurt for 1/10th HP each turn.

SOULHEART.name: Soul-Heart
SOULHEART.description: Boosts Sp. Atk each time a Pokémon faints.

SPEEDBOOST.name: Speed Boost
SPEEDBOOST.description: Speed is raised by two steps at the end of each of its turns.

STAMINA.name: Stamina
STAMINA.description: Boosts Defense by two steps when hit by an attack.

STANCECHANGE.name: Stance Change
STANCECHANGE.description: Changes between Blade and Shield Forme with attacks and King's Shield.

STATIC.name: Static
STATIC.description: Physical attacks against the Pokémon has a 30% chance to cause numbing.

STEELYSPIRIT.name: Steely Spirit
STEELYSPIRIT.description: Powers up Steel-type moves of itself and its allies by 50%.

STRONGJAW.name: Strong Jaw
STRONGJAW.description: Boosts the power of biting moves by 50%.

STURDY.name: Sturdy
STURDY.description: It can't be knocked out with one hit.

SUPERLUCK.name: Super Luck
SUPERLUCK.description: Quadruples the critical hit chance of random crit moves.

SWIFTSWIM.name: Swift Swim
SWIFTSWIM.description: Doubles the Pokémon's Speed in rainstorm.

SYNCHRONIZE.name: Synchronize
SYNCHRONIZE.description: When the Pokémon is given a non-volatile status condition by another Pokémon, that Pokemon also gets that condition.

TANGLINGHAIR.name: Tangling Hair
TANGLINGHAIR.description: Physical moves against it lower the attacker's Speed by three steps.

TECHNICIAN.name: Technician
TECHNICIAN.description: Moves with base power 60 or less deal 50% more damage.

TELEPATHY.name: Telepathy
TELEPATHY.description: Anticipates an ally's attack and dodges it.

THICKFAT.name: Thick Fat
THICKFAT.description: Takes half damage from Fire- and Ice-type moves.

TINTEDLENS.name: Tinted Lens
TINTEDLENS.description: Doubles the damage of "not very effective" moves.

TRIAGE.name: Triage
TRIAGE.description: Gives +3 priority to healing and draining moves.

TRUANT.name: Truant
TRUANT.description: Every other turn, the Pokémon can't use any move but Slack Off.

UNAWARE.name: Unaware
UNAWARE.description: Ignores modified Defense and Sp. Def while attacking, and ignores modified Attack and Sp. Atk while being attacked.

UNBURDEN.name: Unburden
UNBURDEN.description: Doubles the Pokémon's Speed if its held item is consumed or lost.

UNSEENFIST.name: Unseen Fist
UNSEENFIST.description: Physical moves negate all protection effects.

VICTORYSTAR.name: Victory Star
VICTORYSTAR.description: Doubles the Accuracy, critical hit rate, and chance to activate random added effects for its allies and itself.

VITALSPIRIT.name: Vital Spirit
VITALSPIRIT.description: Prevents the Pokémon from falling asleep.

VOLTABSORB.name: Volt Absorb
VOLTABSORB.description: Immune to Electric-type moves and restores 25% of max HP when hit by one.

WANDERINGSPIRIT.name: Wandering Spirit
WANDERINGSPIRIT.description: When the Pokémon is hit by an attack, the Pokémon and the attacker switch abilities.

WATERABSORB.name: Water Absorb
WATERABSORB.description: Immune to Water-type moves and restores 25% of max HP when hit by one.

WATERBUBBLE.name: Water Bubble
WATERBUBBLE.description: Weakens incoming Fire-type moves, and doubles Water-type damage.

WEAKARMOR.name: Weak Armor
WEAKARMOR.description: Physical attacks against the Pokémon raise its Speed by two steps but lower its Defense.

WHITESMOKE.name: White Smoke
WHITESMOKE.description: Prevents stat steps from being lowered (except when self-inflicted).

WIMPOUT.name: Wimp Out
WIMPOUT.description: Cowardly switches out if its HP becomes half or less.

ABOVEITALL.name: Above It All
ABOVEITALL.description: After being attacked, uses Parting Shot to switch out.

ACCUMULATION.name: Accumulation
ACCUMULATION.description: The Pokémon gains twice as many stats from leveling up.

ACIDRAIN.name: Acid Rain
ACIDRAIN.description: At the end of each turn in rainstorm, each Pokémon not immune to rainstorm has their Defense and Sp. Def lowered.

ADAPTIVESKIN.name: Adaptive Skin
ADAPTIVESKIN.description: After being hit, the Pokémon raises either Defense or Sp. Def based on the attack's category. Caps out at +4.

ADRENALINERUSH.name: Adrenaline Rush
ADRENALINERUSH.description: Raises Speed by four steps when its HP is lowered below half.

AERODYNAMIC.name: Aerodynamic
AERODYNAMIC.description: Grants immunity to Flying-type moves and raises Speed if hit by one.

AEROSHELL.name: Aeroshell
AEROSHELL.description: After using a wind move, raises the Pokémon's Defense and Sp. Def. Caps out at +4.

AFROTECTION.name: Afrotection
AFROTECTION.description: Protects the Pokémon from recoil damage. The Pokémon doesn't trigger items, abilities, or effects of targets it hits.

AFTERIMAGE.name: Afterimage
AFTERIMAGE.description: Slips past all types of spikes. Deals 50% more damage to targets that switched in this turn.

AGGRAVATE.name: Aggravate
AGGRAVATE.description: HP-fraction-based damage effects deal 50% more damage to opponents.

ALLCONSUMING.name: All-Consuming
ALLCONSUMING.description: When another Pokémon faints, consumes their item, ability, and stat steps.

ALLTHATGLITTERS.name: All That Glitters
ALLTHATGLITTERS.description: Can hold two different items, if both are Gems.

ANCESTRALDANCE.name: Ancestral Dance
ANCESTRALDANCE.description: Raises Defense and Sp. Def whenever any Pokémon uses a dance move. Caps out at +4.

APPREHENSIVE.name: Apprehensive
APPREHENSIVE.description: Takes 35% less damage in eclipse, except in total eclipse.

APRICORNARMOR.name: Apricorn Armor
APRICORNARMOR.description: Takes 40% less damage from attacks by Pokémon who have a non-volatile status condition.

ARCANEFINALE.name: Arcane Finale
ARCANEFINALE.description: Turns to Finale Form when only unfainted on team. Ability becomes Synchronize.

ARCCONDUCTOR.name: Arc Conductor
ARCCONDUCTOR.description: Inflicts 1/6th max HP damage to the foe when damaged during rainstorm.

ARCHVILLAIN.name: Archvillain
ARCHVILLAIN.description: Boosts the Pokémon's Attack by 50%, but its attacks cannot faint the target.

ARCTICARIETTE.name: Arctic Ariette
ARCTICARIETTE.description: Sound-based attacks turn Ice-type and are boosted by 30%.

ARMORPIERCING.name: Armor Piercing
ARMORPIERCING.description: Deals double damage against Pokémon that have raised defenses or that are protected by a screen.

AROMATIC.name: Aromatic
AROMATIC.description: Uses Aromatherapy if an attack lowers its HP to half or below.

ASSAULTSPINES.name: Assault Spines
ASSAULTSPINES.description: Doubles Sp. Def, but the Pokémon can't use status moves.

ASSISTANT.name: Assistant
ASSISTANT.description: Uses Assist upon entry, using a random move known by a party member.

ASTRALHARVEST.name: Astral Harvest
ASTRALHARVEST.description: During eclipse, it restores its HP by half the damage it deals with attacks.

AURORAPRISM.name: Aurora Prism
AURORAPRISM.description: Attacks this Pokémon uses that don't share a type with it are boosted by 50%. It can't use attacks of its own types.

AUTOPILOT.name: Auto-Pilot
AUTOPILOT.description: At the beginning of every 5th turn, the Pokémon forcibly switches into battle. It chooses which move it will use that turn.

AUTOSTRUCTURE.name: Auto-Structure
AUTOSTRUCTURE.description: At the end of every turn, its stats shift position (Attack-> Defense -> Sp. Atk -> Sp. Def -> Speed -> Attack...)

AUTUMNAL.name: Autumnal
AUTUMNAL.description: Healing on the Pokémon is reversed.

BACKWASH.name: Backwash
BACKWASH.description: Special attacks against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to waterlog the attacker.

BADINFLUENCE.name: Bad Influence
BADINFLUENCE.description: The effect of healing on foes is reversed.

BADLUCK.name: Bad Luck
BADLUCK.description: When free from non-volatile status conditions, non-damaging moves by foes are drawn in.

BADOMEN.name: Bad Omen
BADOMEN.description: Foretold moves hit two turns quicker and deal 30% more damage.

BALLLIGHTNING.name: Ball Lightning
BALLLIGHTNING.description: Deals more damage to targets the faster it is than them. Up to a 50% bonus at double Speed.

BALLMIMIC.name: Ball Mimic
BALLMIMIC.description: Your Poké Balls are 50% more effective.

BARRIERMAKER.name: Barrier Maker
BARRIERMAKER.description: Sets a Reflect for 4 turns upon entering the battle.

BATTLEHARDENED.name: Battle-Hardened
BATTLEHARDENED.description: Raises Defense and Sp. Def by three steps when its HP is lowered below half.

BEGUILING.name: Beguiling
BEGUILING.description: Special attacks against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to dizzy the attacker.

BELLIGERENT.name: Belligerent

BELLOWER.name: Bellower
BELLOWER.description: After using a sound move, all foes are tormented.

BERRYBUNCH.name: Berry Bunch
BERRYBUNCH.description: Can hold two different items, if both are Berries.

BIGBOSS.name: Big Boss
BIGBOSS.description: Boosts Defense by 25%. The Pokémon cannot be flinched.

BITTER.name: Bitter
BITTER.description: Its attacks are critical against frostbitten targets.

BITTERCOLD.name: Bitter Cold

BIZARRE.name: Bizarre
BIZARRE.description: Its special attacks reduce the target's Sp. Def.

BLADEBRAINED.name: Bladebrained

BLINDINGLIGHT.name: Blinding Light

BLISS.name: Bliss
BLISS.description: Increase the EXP gained from battles in which it participates by 50%.

BOTTOMFEEDER.name: Bottom Feeder

BOULDERNEST.name: Boulder Nest

BRAINSCRAMBLE.name: Brain Scramble
BRAINSCRAMBLE.description: Has a 30% chance to dizzy targets when using special moves.

BREAKINGWAVE.name: Breaking Wave
BREAKINGWAVE.description: Slips past hazards. On the first turn, its attacks are always critical.

BREAKTHROUGH.name: Break Through
BREAKTHROUGH.description: Moves ignore immunities due to typing.

BRILLIANTFLURRY.name: Brilliant Flurry
BRILLIANTFLURRY.description: If an attack lowers its HP to half or less, lowers all of the attacker's stats.

BRISK.name: Brisk
BRISK.description: Boosts the power of wind-based moves by 30%.

BRUTEFORCE.name: Brute Force
BRUTEFORCE.description: Its attacks are always physical attacks.

BULLY.name: Bully

BUNKERDOWN.name: Bunker Down
BUNKERDOWN.description: Self-destructing at full health leaves it at 1 HP.

BURDENED.name: Burdened
BURDENED.description: Receives 33% less move damage, but the Pokémon is hurt for 1/10th HP each turn.

BURNOUT.name: Burn Out
BURNOUT.description: Has a 30% chance to burn targets when using physical moves.

BURNSKILL.name: Burn Skill
BURNSKILL.description: Has a 30% chance to burn targets when using special moves.

CANDYVEIL.name: Candy Veil
CANDYVEIL.description: Prevents itself and allies from being poisoned, leeched, or waterlogged.

CASHOUT.name: Cash Out
CASHOUT.description: Upon entry, consumes scattered coins to heal for 1/10th the amount consumed. This can overheal.

CHALLENGER.name: Challenger
CHALLENGER.description: Immune to Fighting-type moves, and raises Attack and Sp. Atk if hit by one.

CHILLEDBODY.name: Chilled Body
CHILLEDBODY.description: Physical moves against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to frostbite the attacker.

CHILLOUT.name: Chill Out
CHILLOUT.description: Has a 30% chance to frostbite targets when using special moves.

CHOREOGRAPHY.name: Choreography
CHOREOGRAPHY.description: Raises Speed whenever any Pokémon uses a dance move.

CHRONICCOLD.name: Chronic Cold
CHRONICCOLD.description: Physical moves have a 30% chance to frostbite targets.

CITYRAZER.name: City Razer
CITYRAZER.description: After knocking out any Pokémon with Waterfall, transforms into its Rampage form. Ability becomes Juggernaut.

CLEANFREAK.name: Clean Freak
CLEANFREAK.description: Boosts move damage by 50% while it has a non-volatile status condition. It suffers double effect from such status conditions.

CLINGY.name: Clingy
CLINGY.description: Prevents foes with non-volatile status conditions from fleeing.

CLOAKING.name: Cloaking
CLOAKING.description: It changes form to match the move it selected.

CLOUDBURST.name: Cloudburst
CLOUDBURST.description: Boosts Sp. Atk and Speed by 30% in rainstorm.

CLOVERSONG.name: Clover Song
CLOVERSONG.description: Sets a Lucky Chant upon entering the battle, protecting from critical hits for 10 turns.

CLUMSYKINESIS.name: Clumsy Kinesis
CLUMSYKINESIS.description: Can hold two items, but drops one when swapping out.

COLDCALCULATION.name: Cold Calculation
COLDCALCULATION.description: Boosts Sp. Attack by 75%, but the Pokémon becomes frostbitten after attacking.

COLDRECEPTION.name: Cold Reception
COLDRECEPTION.description: Immune to Ice-type moves, and raises Attack and Sp. Atk if hit by one.

CONSTRICTOR.name: Constrictor
CONSTRICTOR.description: When hit with a physical move, traps and damages the attacker for three turns.

COREPROVENANCE.name: Core Provenance
COREPROVENANCE.description: Using or being hit by a physical move leaves a rock on the field. Status moves collect them, healing by 1/4th each.

COSTUMECHANGE.name: Costume Change
COSTUMECHANGE.description: Changes to the form of your choosing after switching out.

COTTONDECOY.name: Cotton Decoy
COTTONDECOY.description: Upon entry, creates a substitute from 1/4th of its HP.

COUNTERFLOW.name: Counter Flow
COUNTERFLOW.description: When hit with a special move, hits back instantly with Breach.

CURSEDTAIL.name: Cursed Tail
CURSEDTAIL.description: When a foe hits the Pokémon, they are warned. If they do it again, they become cursed.

CYNIC.name: Cynic
CYNIC.description: Immune to Dragon-type, Fairy-type and Ghost-type attacks.

DARING.name: Daring
DARING.description: When this Pokémon gains a non-volatile status condition, its Attack is raised by three steps.

DARKENEDSKIES.name: Darkened Skies
DARKENEDSKIES.description: Powers up the Pokémon's Dark-type moves by 50% in sandstorm.

DARKSCALECLOUD.name: Darkscale Cloud
DARKSCALECLOUD.description: While the Pokémon is below half health, its attacks poisons those hit.

DARTER.name: Darter
DARTER.description: Takes 30% less move damage if a Tailwind is blowing.

DAUNTLESS.name: Dauntless
DAUNTLESS.description: Boosts Attack and Sp. Atk after knocking out any Pokémon.

DAWNFALL.name: Dawnfall
DAWNFALL.description: On the first turn, its attacks burn the target.

DEBRISFIELD.name: Debris Field
DEBRISFIELD.description: Immune to non-volatile status conditions due to its hard shell. Boosts Sp. Atk and Speed by 30% in sandstorm.

DECONTAMINATION.name: Decontamination
DECONTAMINATION.description: Prevents Bug- or Poison-type moves during moonglow.

DEEPSTING.name: Deep Sting
DEEPSTING.description: Boosts Attack by 50%, but physical moves deal 25% damage back as recoil.

DEEPTEETH.name: Deep Teeth
DEEPTEETH.description: Foes aren't released from its trapping moves even when the Pokémon leaves the field.

DELAYEDREACTION.name: Delayed Reaction
DELAYEDREACTION.description: 33% of all move damage taken by the Pokémon is instead taken at the end of the next turn.

DESERTARMOR.name: Desert Armor
DESERTARMOR.description: Doubles the Pokémon's Defense in a sandstorm.

DESERTSCAVENGER.name: Desert Scavenger
DESERTSCAVENGER.description: Restores the Pokémon's HP based on damage taken by others from sandstorm.

DESERTSPIRIT.name: Desert Spirit
DESERTSPIRIT.description: The Pokémon is immune to Ground-type moves and takes 20% less damage in sandstorm.

DESICCATE.name: Desiccate
DESICCATE.description: Prevents Water- or Grass-type moves during sandstorm.

DETERRENT.name: Deterrent
DETERRENT.description: Enemies which swap in take damage equal to 1/8th their HP.

DIRECTCURRENT.name: Direct Current
DIRECTCURRENT.description: At the end of each turn, its Sp. Atk is lowered. Then, you choose to raise its Speed or heal it for 1/5th HP.

DIREDIVERSION.name: Dire Diversion
DIREDIVERSION.description: It can avoid being knocked out by sacrificing its held item.

DISCONNECTION.name: Disconnection
DISCONNECTION.description: On the first turn, its attacks numb the target.

DISORIENTING.name: Disorienting
DISORIENTING.description: Physical attacks against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to dizzy the attacker.

DOMINATING.name: Dominating
DOMINATING.description: After knocking out any Pokémon, raises its Attack and Defense.

DOMINEERING.name: Domineering
DOMINEERING.description: Reduces move damage taken by 50% when HP is full. Can't be dizzied.

DOUBLECHECK.name: Double Check
DOUBLECHECK.description: Deals 50% more damage to targets who have already taken damage this turn.

DRAGONSBLOOD.name: Dragon's Blood
DRAGONSBLOOD.description: Reduces the damage of each hit against it by an amount equal to its level.

DRAGONSLAYER.name: Dragon Slayer
DRAGONSLAYER.description: Immune to Dragon-type moves. Deals double damage to Dragon-types.

DRAMATICLIGHTING.name: Dramatic Lighting

DREAMWEAVER.name: Dream Weaver
DREAMWEAVER.description: Raises Sp. Atk by two steps whenever any battler falls asleep.

DREAMYHAZE.name: Dreamy Haze
DREAMYHAZE.description: If an attack lowers its HP to half or less, the attacker becomes drowsy.

DREARYCLOUDS.name: Dreary Clouds
DREARYCLOUDS.description: Move damage that's decreased by rainstorm is decreased twice as much.

DRIFTINGMIST.name: Drifting Mist
DRIFTINGMIST.description: Creates Grey Mist for three turns when entering the battlefield.

DYNAMICENTRANCE.name: Dynamic Entrance
DYNAMICENTRANCE.description: Speed is doubled on the first turn.

DYNAMO.name: Dynamo
DYNAMO.description: Whenever it uses a status move, becomes energy charged, doubling the power of its next Electric-type attack.

EARSPLITTING.name: Ear-Splitting
EARSPLITTING.description: Boosts power of the Pokémon's sound-based moves by 50%.

EARTHSHAKER.name: Earthshaker
EARTHSHAKER.description: In sandstorm, the Pokémon's Attack is boosted by 30%.

ECCENTRIC.name: Eccentric
ECCENTRIC.description: If its stats would be changed, instead they're changed half as much in the opposite direction (rounded up).

ECHO.name: Echo
ECHO.description: Repeats another Pokémon's sound and pulse moves immediately at 50% power.

EFFLORESCENT.name: Efflorescent

EMERGENCYPOWER.name: Emergency Power
EMERGENCYPOWER.description: Uses Lightning Dance if an attack lowers its HP to half or below.

EMOTIONAURA.name: Emotion Aura
EMOTIONAURA.description: Upon entry, creates an Emotion Room for four turns, switching Abilities every turn.

ENERGETIC.name: Energetic
ENERGETIC.description: Can't be numbed, waterlogged, or have its Speed reduced.

ENVY.name: Envy
ENVY.description: The Pokémon's moves have priority against single targets with increased stats.

EPHEMERATE.name: Ephemerate
EPHEMERATE.description: Eclipse counts down twice as quickly.

EXCAVATOR.name: Excavator
EXCAVATOR.description: Dig and Undermine deal 50% more damage.

EXORCIST.name: Exorcist
EXORCIST.description: Takes half damage from Psychic- and Ghost-type attacks.

EXOTHERMENGINE.name: Exotherm Engine
EXOTHERMENGINE.description: Boosts Speed by 50% but the Pokémon is locked into the first move they use.

EXTORTER.name: Extorter
EXTORTER.description: At low health, eats other battlers' low-health triggered berries.

EXTRASCOOP.name: Extra Scoop
EXTRASCOOP.description: Upon entry, the Pokémon heals itself for 1/4th max HP. This can overheal.

EXTREMEPOWER.name: Extreme Power
EXTREMEPOWER.description: Increases Attack by 50%, but the Pokémon is hurt for 1/10th HP each turn.

EXTREMEVOLTAGE.name: Extreme Voltage
EXTREMEVOLTAGE.description: Increases Sp. Atk by 50%, but the Pokémon is hurt for 1/10th HP each turn.

EXTREMOPHILE.name: Extremophile
EXTREMOPHILE.description: Heals by 1/8th of its max HP each turn if in eclipse.

FAEVEIL.name: Fae Veil
FAEVEIL.description: Prevents itself and allies from being burned, frostbitten, or numbed.

FASCINATE.name: Fascinate
FASCINATE.description: Upon entry, lowers the foe's Sp. Atk stat by two steps.

FASHIONABLE.name: Fashionable
FASHIONABLE.description: Can hold two different items, if one is clothing and the other is not.

FATCHANCE.name: Fat Chance
FATCHANCE.description: Raises all of its stats whenever it knocks out a Pokémon with a critical hit.

FATIGUED.name: Fatigued

FEATHERCOAT.name: Feather Coat
FEATHERCOAT.description: Takes half damage from Ice- and Flying-type attacks.

FEEDBACK.name: Feedback

FEELTHEBURN.name: Feel the Burn
FEELTHEBURN.description: Boosts Attack by 75%, but the Pokémon becomes burned after attacking.

FELLOMEN.name: Fell Omen
FELLOMEN.description: During eclipse, gets a 30% boost to Sp. Atk.

FEROCIOUS.name: Ferocious
FEROCIOUS.description: Double the Pokémon's Speed if any enemy is below half health.

FERROFLUID.name: Ferrofluid
FERROFLUID.description: Takes 30% less damage in a rainstorm.

FIERYSPIRIT.name: Fiery Spirit
FIERYSPIRIT.description: Special moves against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to burn the attacker.

FIESTA.name: Fiesta
FIESTA.description: Heals by 1/8th HP whenever any Pokémon uses a dance or sound move.

FIGHTINGVIGOR.name: Fighting Vigor
FIGHTINGVIGOR.description: Heals 1/16th HP every turn. Protected from being numbed or waterlogged.

FILTHY.name: Filthy
FILTHY.description: Immune to Poison-type moves, and boosts Defense and Sp. Def when hit by one.

FINESUGAR.name: Fine Sugar

FIREFESTIVAL.name: Fire Festival

FIREFIGHTER.name: Firefighter
FIREFIGHTER.description: Immune to Fire-type moves, and raises Attack and Sp. Atk if hit by one.

FITTOSURVIVE.name: Fit to Survive

FLAMEWINGS.name: Flame Wings
FLAMEWINGS.description: Flying-type attacks have a 40% chance to burn.

FLASHFREEZE.name: Flash Freeze
FLASHFREEZE.description: On the first turn, its attacks frostbite the target.

FLEXIBLE.name: Flexible
FLEXIBLE.description: Attacks this Pokémon uses that don't share a type with it are boosted by 30%.

FLOURISHING.name: Flourishing
FLOURISHING.description: Grows at the end of each turn, slowing down but improving other stats.

FLUSTERFLOCK.name: Fluster Flock
FLUSTERFLOCK.description: Doubles Attack, but the Pokémon becomes dizzy after attacking.

FLUTTERTOTEM.name: Flutter Totem

FLYBY.name: Fly By

FLYTRAP.name: Flytrap
FLYTRAP.description: Grants immunity to Bug-type moves, and raises Attack and Sp. Atk when hit by one.

FOGTOTEM.name: Fog Totem

FOLLOWTHROUGH.name: Follow Through
FOLLOWTHROUGH.description: Raises Speed by two steps after knocking out any Pokémon.

FOOLHARDY.name: Foolhardy
FOOLHARDY.description: Immune to Psychic-type moves, and raises Attack and Sp. Atk if hit by one.

FORCEREVERSAL.name: Force Reversal

FOREMAN.name: Foreman

FORTIFIED.name: Fortified
FORTIFIED.description: Take 30% less damage from attacks on turns when it hasn't moved yet.

FREERIDE.name: Free Ride
FREERIDE.description: Raises other allies' Speed by two steps upon entering the battle.

FREESTYLE.name: Freestyle

FRIGIDREFLECTION.name: Frigid Reflection
FRIGIDREFLECTION.description: When hit with a special move, hits back instantly with that same move.

FROSTFANGED.name: Frostfanged
FROSTFANGED.description: Boosts Attack and Speed by 30% in hail.

FROSTPITALITY.name: Frostpitality
FROSTPITALITY.description: Prevents the foe from escaping during hail.

FROSTSCATTER.name: Frost Scatter
FROSTSCATTER.description: Summons a hail for four turns when hit by an attack.

FROSTWINGS.name: Frost Wings
FROSTWINGS.description: Flying-type attacks have a 40% chance to frostbite.

FRUSTRATE.name: Frustrate
FRUSTRATE.description: Upon entry, lowers the foe's Speed stat by two steps.

FUELHUNGRY.name: Fuel Hungry
FUELHUNGRY.description: Boosts Attack by 30%, but lowers Attack after using a physical move.

FULLBLUBBER.name: Full Blubber
FULLBLUBBER.description: Immune to Fire-type and Ice-type moves.

FULLMOONBLADE.name: Full Moon Blade
FULLMOONBLADE.description: Doubled Attack during the turn of a Full Moon.

FUMIGATE.name: Fumigate
FUMIGATE.description: Random added effects of wind-based moves are +50% more likely to occur.

GALEFORCE.name: Gale Force
GALEFORCE.description: Boosts the power of wind-based moves by 50%.

GARGANTUAN.name: Gargantuan
GARGANTUAN.description: Completely protects allies from foes' multi-target moves.

GAUSSAFTERSHOCK.name: Gauss Aftershock
GAUSSAFTERSHOCK.description: Pokémon that swap in for this have their Speed raised and their PP fully restored.

GILD.name: Gild

GLASSFIRING.name: Glass Firing
GLASSFIRING.description: Immune to Fire-type moves and raises Defense and Sp. Def if hit by one.

GNAWING.name: Gnawing
GNAWING.description: Random added effects of bite attacks are +50% more likely likely to occur.

GORGING.name: Gorging

GOURMAND.name: Gourmand
GOURMAND.description: Eats pinch berries earlier than normal. Gets a random pinch berry at the end of each turn if it has no item.

GRAVITAS.name: Gravitas
GRAVITAS.description: Upon entry, intensifies gravity for five turns.

GRIPSTRENGTH.name: Grip Strength
GRIPSTRENGTH.description: Moves that bind the opponent deal 50% more damage (on the initial hit).

GRIT.name: Grit
GRIT.description: Boosts Sp. Def by two steps when hit by an attack.

GROOVY.name: Groovy
GROOVY.description: Raises Attack whenever any Pokémon uses a dance move.

GROTESQUEVITALS.name: Grotesque Vitals
GROTESQUEVITALS.description: Heals 1/16th HP every turn. Protected from being poisoned.

GYRESPINNER.name: Gyre Spinner
GYRESPINNER.description: Upon entry, traps each opponent in a whirlpool for two turns.

HARBINGER.name: Harbinger
HARBINGER.description: Summons eclipse for four turns when it enters battle.

HARDAS.name: Hard As
HARDAS.description: If an attack lowers the Pokémon's HP to half or less, the attacker becomes fractured.

HARDFALL.name: Hard Fall
HARDFALL.description: Deals 30% more move damage to Pokémon that are taller than it.

HARSH.name: Harsh
HARSH.description: Its attacks are critical against burned targets.

HASTY.name: Hasty
HASTY.description: When this Pokémon gains a non-volatile status condition, its Speed is raised by three steps.

HEADACHE.name: Headache
HEADACHE.description: Doubles Sp. Atk, but the Pokémon becomes dizzy after attacking.

HEARTLESS.name: Heartless

HEARTOFJUSTICE.name: Heart of Justice
HEARTOFJUSTICE.description: Immune to Dark-type moves, and boosts Attack and Sp. Atk when hit by one.

HEATSAVOR.name: Heat Savor
HEATSAVOR.description: Heals by 1/8th of its max HP each turn if in sunshine.

HEATVEIL.name: Heat Veil
HEATVEIL.description: Doubles the Pokémon's Sp. Def in sunshine.

HEAVYDUTYHOOVES.name: Heavy Duty Hooves

HELIOCENTRISM.name: Heliocentrism
HELIOCENTRISM.description: Prevents the foe from escaping during gravity.

HERBALIST.name: Herbalist
HERBALIST.description: Can hold two different items, if both are Herbs.

HERDING.name: Herding
HERDING.description: Wild Pokémon are more likely to appear in pairs and to be species you've never caught before.

HEROICFINALE.name: Heroic Finale
HEROICFINALE.description: Turns to Finale Form when only unfainted on team. Ability becomes Inner Focus.

HIGHRISE.name: High-rise
HIGHRISE.description: The Pokémon and its allies are immune to weather downsides.

HOLIDAYCHEER.name: Holiday Cheer
HOLIDAYCHEER.description: When entering battle, heals self and allies for 25% of their max health.

HONORABLE.name: Honorable
HONORABLE.description: Lowers priority of status moves used by any Pokémon.

HOOLIGAN.name: Hooligan
HOOLIGAN.description: Powers up recoil and sound moves by 30%.

HUBRIS.name: Hubris
HUBRIS.description: Raises Sp. Atk after knocking out any Pokémon.

HUGGABLE.name: Huggable
HUGGABLE.description: When hit by a move with 95 or more base power, hits back instantly with Nuzzle.

HYBRIDFIGHTER.name: Hybrid Fighter
HYBRIDFIGHTER.description: Punches, Kicks, and Bites combo together to create special effects.

HYPERSPEED.name: Hyper Speed
HYPERSPEED.description: Doubles Speed. Dashes to avoid hazards when entering.

ICEBLOCK.name: Ice Block
ICEBLOCK.description: It can avoid being knocked out by using its face. The face then melts.

ICEQUEEN.name: Ice Queen
ICEQUEEN.description: During hail, it restores its HP by half the damage it deals with attacks.

IGNITIONCYCLE.name: Ignition Cycle
IGNITIONCYCLE.description: Each turn, raises Speed by three steps and loses HP. If Speed was maxed, instead Speed and HP are reset.

ILLUMINANCE.name: Illuminance
ILLUMINANCE.description: Boosts Sp. Atk by 30% in moonglow.

IMPERIOUS.name: Imperious
IMPERIOUS.description: Raises Speed by four steps when a stat is lowered by a foe.

IMPERVIOUS.name: Impervious
IMPERVIOUS.description: Prevents stat steps from being lowered (except when self-inflicted). Protects from critical hits.

IMPETUOUS.name: Impetuous
IMPETUOUS.description: Special attacks against the Pokémon raise its Speed by two steps but lower its Sp. Def.

IMPRESSIONABLE.name: Impressionable
IMPRESSIONABLE.description: Its same-type attack bonus is based on its party members rather than itself.

IMPULSIVE.name: Impulsive
IMPULSIVE.description: When this Pokémon gains a non-volatile status condition, its Sp. Atk is raised by three steps.

INCOGNITO.name: Incognito

INDESTRUCTIBLE.name: Indestructible
INDESTRUCTIBLE.description: After being attacked, gains immunity to that move's type but loses other morphed immunities.

INDUSTRIALIZE.name: Industrialize
INDUSTRIALIZE.description: Immune to Steel-type moves and raises Speed if hit by one.

INEXORABLE.name: Inexorable

INFECTED.name: Infected

INNERLIGHT.name: Inner Light
INNERLIGHT.description: Summons sunshine for four turns when hit by an attack.

INSIGHTAURA.name: Insight Aura
INSIGHTAURA.description: Upon entry, creates an Insight Room for four turns, giving everyone a fifth move.

INTOXICATE.name: Intoxicate
INTOXICATE.description: Special moves have a 30% chance to poison targets.

INTROVERT.name: Introvert
INTROVERT.description: Takes 30% less damage until it uses an attack.

INVESTIGATOR.name: Investigator
INVESTIGATOR.description: At the beginning of each turn, gives clues about a foe's plan.

IRONHEEL.name: Iron Heel
IRONHEEL.description: Boosts the power of kicking moves by 30%.

IRONSTORM.name: Iron Storm
IRONSTORM.description: Causes sandstorm to deal double damage and increase Sp. Def of Rock-types by 2.0x instead of 1.5x.

IRREFUTABLE.name: Irrefutable
IRREFUTABLE.description: Raises Attack by two steps after dealing not-very-effective or barely-effective damage.

JOYOUSSORROW.name: Joyous Sorrow
JOYOUSSORROW.description: Uses Wish after knocking out any Pokémon.

JUGGERNAUT.name: Juggernaut
JUGGERNAUT.description: Ignores Abilities that would affect its moves or activate after hitting the target.

KARMA.name: Karma
KARMA.description: If an attack lowers the Pokémon's HP to half or less, the attacker becomes jinxed.

KELPLINK.name: Kelp Link
KELPLINK.description: Physical moves against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to leech the attacker.

KICKBACK.name: Kickback
KICKBACK.description: Rather than take recoil damage, it swaps out, and its replacement takes that damage.

KILLJOY.name: Killjoy
KILLJOY.description: Pokémon can't dance or use sound-based moves.

KLEPTOMANIAC.name: Kleptomaniac
KLEPTOMANIAC.description: Uses Snatch upon entry, stealing self-targeting status moves.

KNUCKLEDUSTER.name: Knuckleduster
KNUCKLEDUSTER.description: Boosts the power of punching moves by 50%.

LARDER.name: Larder
LARDER.description: At end of turn, regenerates its previously-used berry.

LASTGASP.name: Last Gasp
LASTGASP.description: Cannot take damage or be switched out. Hears Perish Song upon entering, ensuring its demise.

LATEBLOOMER.name: Late Bloomer
LATEBLOOMER.description: Deals 30% more damage when it's slower than the target.

LEVIATHAN.name: Leviathan
LEVIATHAN.description: Protected from critical hits. Can't be burned or frostbitten.

LIFELINE.name: Lifeline
LIFELINE.description: At the end of each turn, heals self by 1/20 and a party member by the amount the Pokémon was healed.

LIGHTTRICK.name: Light Trick
LIGHTTRICK.description: Doubled Speed if any enemy has a non-volatile status condition.

LIMINAL.name: Liminal

LINEBACKER.name: Linebacker
LINEBACKER.description: Doubles the damage and recoil of recoil moves.

LIVEFAST.name: Live Fast
LIVEFAST.description: Boosts Speed by 50%, but the Pokémon is hurt for 1/10th HP each turn.

LIVINGARMOR.name: Living Armor
LIVINGARMOR.description: Protected against critical hits. Heals 1/12th HP every turn if hit by an attack.

LONGODDS.name: Long Odds

LONGRECEIVER.name: Long Receiver
LONGRECEIVER.description: Copies the Ability of the Pokémon it switches in to replace.

LOUD.name: Loud
LOUD.description: Boosts power of sound-based moves by 30%.

LOUDSLEEPER.name: Loud Sleeper
LOUDSLEEPER.description: When hit while asleep, hits back instantly with Snore.

LUNARIOT.name: Luna Riot
LUNARIOT.description: Summons moonglow for four turns when hit by an attack.

LUXURYTASTE.name: Luxury Taste
LUXURYTASTE.description: At end of turn, heals 1/12th HP if holding a clothing item.

LYCANTHROPE.name: Lycanthrope
LYCANTHROPE.description: Transforms into Midnight Form at the Full Moon. Ability becomes No Guard.

MAESTRO.name: Maestro
MAESTRO.description: The Pokémon's Speed is doubled while using Sound-based moves.

MAGICSHIELD.name: Magic Shield
MAGICSHIELD.description: Negates enemy status moves that target the Pokémon or create hazards around it.

MAGNETTRAP.name: Magnet Trap
MAGNETTRAP.description: Prevents foes whose Sp. Atk is less than its from fleeing.

MALICE.name: Malice
MALICE.description: If an attack lowers the Pokémon's HP to half or less, the attacker becomes cursed.

MALICIOUSGLOW.name: Malicious Glow
MALICIOUSGLOW.description: When attacking during moonglow, uses the target's Attack and Sp. Atk instead of its own.

MARINE.name: Marine

MARINEMENACE.name: Marine Menace
MARINEMENACE.description: Dive and Depth Charge deal 50% more damage.

MARTIALDISCIPLINE.name: Martial Discipline

MASSATTACK.name: Mass Attack
MASSATTACK.description: All Pokémon's damage is decreased proportional to their health remaining.

MENTALBLOCK.name: Mental Block
MENTALBLOCK.description: The Pokémon can't be Taunted, Encored, Tormented, Heal Blocked, Disabled, Barred, Dizzied, or Flinched.

MENTALDAMAGE.name: Mental Damage
MENTALDAMAGE.description: Disables the opponent's most recently-used move for two turns upon hitting it.

METEORIC.name: Meteoric
METEORIC.description: Boosts the Pokémon's Speed by 50% in sandstorm or hail.

MIDDLEWAY.name: Middle Way
MIDDLEWAY.description: Boosts Attack by 50% if it used a special move last turn, or boosts Sp. Atk if physical.

MIDNIGHTOIL.name: Midnight Oil
MIDNIGHTOIL.description: Using a status move in moonglow extends the weather by a turn.

MIDNIGHTSUN.name: Midnight Sun
MIDNIGHTSUN.description: Powers up the Pokémon's Dark-type moves by 50% in sunshine.

MISTFORM.name: Mist Form
MISTFORM.description: Slips past hazards. Takes 50% less damage if it switched in this turn.

MOISTSKIN.name: Moist Skin
MOISTSKIN.description: If an attack lowers its HP to half or less, waterlogs the attacker.

MONKEYMISCHIEF.name: Monkey Mischief
MONKEYMISCHIEF.description: When hit by another Pokémon, destroys one of their items.

MOONBASKING.name: Moon Basking
MOONBASKING.description: Heals 1/8th of its max HP each turn if in moonglow.

MOONBLANKET.name: Moon Blanket
MOONBLANKET.description: The Pokémon and its allies take 25% less move damage during moonglow.

MOONGAZE.name: Moon Gaze
MOONGAZE.description: Summons moonglow for four turns when it enters battle.

MOONLIGHTER.name: Moonlighter
MOONLIGHTER.description: When hit in moonglow, steals the attacker's item, or knocks it away.

MOTHBURGLAR.name: Moth Burglar
MOTHBURGLAR.description: Hits opponent with Thief when withdrawn from battle.

MUPROTOCOL.name: MU Protocol
MUPROTOCOL.description: Immune to the type of the memory disc it holds.

MUTABLE.name: Mutable
MUTABLE.description: It changes type to that of the move it's about to use. This works only once each time the Pokémon enters battle.

MYSTICFIST.name: Mystic Fist
MYSTICFIST.description: Boosts the power of punching moves by 30%, and makes them special when that would be more effective.

NEEDLEFUR.name: Needle Fur
NEEDLEFUR.description: Attackers lose 1/10th of their HP. If the Pokémon is below half health, attackers lose 1/5th instead.

NERVENUMBER.name: Nerve Number
NERVENUMBER.description: Special moves have a 30% chance to numb targets.

NESTING.name: Nesting
NESTING.description: Heals 1/12th HP per turn if there's a weather. Immune to weather downsides.

NEUROTOXIN.name: Neurotoxin
NEUROTOXIN.description: While the Pokémon is unfainted (in battle or switched out), poisoned foes also suffer from dizzy.

NIGHTOWL.name: Night Owl
NIGHTOWL.description: Boosts Speed by 50% in moonglow. Can't miss during moonglow.

NIGHTSTALKER.name: Night Stalker
NIGHTSTALKER.description: In moonglow, Attack is boosted by 50%, but the Pokémon is hurt for 1/10th HP each turn.

NIGHTVISION.name: Night Vision
NIGHTVISION.description: During moonglow, Speed is boosted by 50% and twice as likely to crit.

NOBLEBLADE.name: Noble Blade
NOBLEBLADE.description: Deals no damage to a target while they are using a status move.

NOHOPE.name: No Hope
NOHOPE.description: Prevents foes whose Attack is less than its from fleeing.

NOXIOUS.name: Noxious
NOXIOUS.description: Reduces each other Pokémon's HP by 1/12th at the end of each turn.

NUMBINGTOUCH.name: Numbing Touch
NUMBINGTOUCH.description: Physical moves have a 30% chance to numb targets.

OCULAR.name: Ocular
OCULAR.description: Boosts the Accuracy of its allies and itself by 50%.

ODDITY.name: Oddity
ODDITY.description: Upon entry, creates an Odd Room for four turns, swapping offensive and defensive stats.

OFFENSIVE.name: Offensive
OFFENSIVE.description: On the first turn, its attacks cause the target to flinch.

ONTHEWIND.name: On the Wind
ONTHEWIND.description: Sets a Tailwind for four turns upon entering the battle, increasing Speed.

OPTIMIZEDALLOY.name: Optimized Alloy
OPTIMIZEDALLOY.description: Prevents stat steps from being lowered (except when self-inflicted). The Pokémon's weight is doubled.

OUTRIDER.name: Outrider
OUTRIDER.description: After knocking out any Pokémon, raises its Attack and Speed.

OVERCHARGE.name: Overcharge
OVERCHARGE.description: After knocking out any Pokémon, raises its Sp. Atk and Speed.

OVERFLOWINGHEART.name: Overflowing Heart
OVERFLOWINGHEART.description: Copies the base stats of the Pokémon it switches in to replace.

OVERTHINKING.name: Overthinking
OVERTHINKING.description: Boosts Sp. Atk by 30%, but lowers Sp. Atk after using a special move.

OVERWHELM.name: Overwhelm
OVERWHELM.description: Boosts Sp. Atk by 30% in rainstorm.

OXYGENATION.name: Oxygenation
OXYGENATION.description: Heals the Pokémon's non-volatile status conditions each turn if in sunshine.

PACIFIST.name: Pacifist
PACIFIST.description: The Pokémon refuses to fight. However, it gathers extra candy when trainers flee.

PALACEGUARD.name: Palace Guard
PALACEGUARD.description: The Pokémon receives 33% less move damage if there is an active Room.

PARANOID.name: Paranoid
PARANOID.description: Doubles Sp. Def. The Pokémon takes double damage from Psychic-type moves.

PECKINGORDER.name: Pecking Order
PECKINGORDER.description: Immune to Flying-type moves and deals 50% more damage with them.

PERENNIALPAYLOAD.name: Perennial Payload
PERENNIALPAYLOAD.description: After fainting from exploding, revives after six turns.

PERFECTIONIST.name: Perfectionist
PERFECTIONIST.description: The Pokémon's hits deal half damage unless they are critical.

PERFECTLUCK.name: Perfect Luck
PERFECTLUCK.description: Maximizes the frequency of multi-strike moves. Always deals critical hits.

PERSISTENTGROWTH.name: Persistent Growth
PERSISTENTGROWTH.description: At the end of each of its turns, Speed is lowered but every other stat is raised.

PESTILENT.name: Pestilent
PESTILENT.description: While the Pokémon is below half health, its attacks leech those hit.

PETRIFYING.name: Petrifying
PETRIFYING.description: Special attacks against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to cause numbing.

PETTY.name: Petty
PETTY.description: Whenever a foe raises their stats, the Pokémon follows suit.

PHASESHIFT.name: Phase Shift
PHASESHIFT.description: The Pokémon's moves deal 50% more damage if they're a different type than last.

PLACIDITY.name: Placidity
PLACIDITY.description: Takes no damage from non-volatile status conditions.

PLANARVEIL.name: Planar Veil
PLANARVEIL.description: Sets screens for two more turns.

PLASMAGLOBE.name: Plasma Globe
PLASMAGLOBE.description: Attacks against the Pokémon deal 50% more damage, but the attacker takes 100% recoil.

PLOTARMOR.name: Plot Armor
PLOTARMOR.description: During eclipse, immune to non-volatile status conditions and stat reductions.

PLURIPOTENCE.name: Pluripotence
PLURIPOTENCE.description: At the first chance, copies an opponent's species' legal Abilities.

POISONABSORB.name: Poison Absorb
POISONABSORB.description: Immune to Poison-type moves and restores 25% of max HP if hit by one.

POISONPUNISH.name: Poison Punish
POISONPUNISH.description: Special attacks against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to poison the attacker.

POLARIZING.name: Polarizing
POLARIZING.description: Upon entry, creates a Polarized Room for four turns, exaggerating type matchups.

POORCONDUCT.name: Poor Conduct
POORCONDUCT.description: Upon switch out, lowers the foe's Attack and Sp. Atk stat by insulting them.

POWERLIFTER.name: Power Lifter
POWERLIFTER.description: Its physical attacks go last but force the target to switch out after use.

PREDATION.name: Predation
PREDATION.description: Has a 30% chance to leech targets when using physical moves.

PRESSUREVALVE.name: Pressure Valve
PRESSUREVALVE.description: Right before the Pokémon is attacked, the attacker's stat changes are reset.

PUNISHER.name: Punisher
PUNISHER.description: Special moves against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to leech the attacker.

PUREENERGY.name: Pure Energy
PUREENERGY.description: Raises the Pokémon's Sp. Atk by 50%, including Style Values and other bonuses.

PURERAGE.name: Pure Rage
PURERAGE.description: The Pokémon's Dragon-type hits deal additional damage equal to half the Pokémon's level.

PUZZLING.name: Puzzling
PUZZLING.description: Upon entry, creates a Puzzle Room for four turns, swapping base Attack and Sp. Atk.

QUARRELSOME.name: Quarrelsome
QUARRELSOME.description: Both deals and takes double damage on its first full turn out in battle.

QUILLERINSTINCT.name: Quiller Instinct
QUILLERINSTINCT.description: Releases a layer of Spikes when hit by an attack.

RAINPRISM.name: Rain Prism
RAINPRISM.description: Powers up Fairy-type moves by 50% in rainstorm.

RAMPROW.name: Ram Prow
RAMPROW.description: Ignores screens, Substitute, and Abilities that would affect its moves.

RATTLEEM.name: Rattle 'Em
RATTLEEM.description: Moves that can flinch are 50% more likely. Deals 50% more damage to Pokémon with flinch immunity.

RAZORSEDGE.name: Razor's Edge
RAZORSEDGE.description: Boosts the power of blade moves by 30%. They're twice as likely to crit.

REALIST.name: Realist
REALIST.description: Takes half damage from Dragon-, Fairy-, and Ghost-type attacks.

REAPWHATYOUSOW.name: Reap What You Sow
REAPWHATYOUSOW.description: If the Pokémon faints from Perish Song, it is revived in a new form.

REAWAKENEDPOWER.name: Reawakened Power
REAWAKENEDPOWER.description: Maximizes Sp. Atk when its HP is lowered below half.

RECLAMATION.name: Reclamation
RECLAMATION.description: After knocking out any Pokémon, regenerates its previously-used item.

RECON.name: Recon
RECON.description: Before using a status move against a single foe, lowers their Sp. Def by two steps.

REFRACTIVE.name: Refractive
REFRACTIVE.description: Pulse moves change the Pokémon's secondary type and their power is boosted by 30%.

REFRESHMENTS.name: Refreshments
REFRESHMENTS.description: Upon entry during sunshine, heals the lowest HP ally or self by 33%.

REFUGE.name: Refuge
REFUGE.description: Pokémon that swap in for this have their non-volatile status conditions healed, and take 30% less damage that turn.

RELUCTANTBLADE.name: Reluctant Blade
RELUCTANTBLADE.description: When hit with a physical move, hits back instantly with Leafage.

RENDINGCLAWS.name: Rending Claws
RENDINGCLAWS.description: Critical hits lower all of the victim's stats.

RESOLUTE.name: Resolute
RESOLUTE.description: Immune to Dark-type and Bug-type moves.

RESONANT.name: Resonant
RESONANT.description: Moves that hit multiple targets deal 25% more damage instead of 25% less.

ROAST.name: Roast
ROAST.description: When the Pokémon eats a Berry, it raises its Attack and Sp. Atk by two steps.

ROCKBODY.name: Rock Body
ROCKBODY.description: Heals 1/8th of its max HP each turn during sandstorm.

ROCKCLIMBER.name: Rock Climber
ROCKCLIMBER.description: Immune to Rock-type moves and to Stealth Rock, and raises Speed whenever one would hit it.

ROOTED.name: Rooted
ROOTED.description: Gets 50% more healing from all sources.

ROYALMAJESTY.name: Royal Majesty
ROYALMAJESTY.description: Makes foes unable to use priority moves.

RUGGED.name: Rugged
RUGGED.description: Immune to Fighting-type and Rock-type moves. Prevents Stealth Rock damage.

RUGGEDSCALES.name: Rugged Scales
RUGGEDSCALES.description: Protected from random added effects. Takes 30% less damage from moves with random added effects.

RUINOUS.name: Ruinous
RUINOUS.description: All Pokémon deal 40% more move damage.

RUNNINGFREE.name: Running Free
RUNNINGFREE.description: Can't be numbed, waterlogged, trapped, or have its Speed lowered.

RUSTWRACK.name: Rust & Wrack
RUSTWRACK.description: The Pokémon is also Steel-type, but it takes 15% more damage from moves.

SANDBURST.name: Sand Burst
SANDBURST.description: Summons a sandstorm for four turns when hit by an attack.

SANDSMACABRE.name: Sands Macabre
SANDSMACABRE.description: When it attacks from underground in sandstorm, it'll transform into Reaper form.

SANDSNIPER.name: Sand Sniper
SANDSNIPER.description: Boosts the Pokémon's Speed by 50% in sandstorm. Can't miss during sandstorm.

SANDWORNAUGER.name: Sandworn Auger
SANDWORNAUGER.description: During sandstorm, the Pokémon's Speed is boosted by 50% and twice as likely to crit.

SAPPER.name: Sapper
SAPPER.description: Upon entry, traps each opponent in a sand tomb for two turns.

SATURATER.name: Saturater
SATURATER.description: Special moves have a 30% chance to waterlog targets.

SATURNALSKY.name: Saturnal Sky
SATURNALSKY.description: Changes the weather to ring eclipse, which heralds the total ring eclipse. Lingers for 3 turns after leaving.

SCATHINGSYZYGY.name: Scathing Syzygy
SCATHINGSYZYGY.description: Boosts all of the Pokémon's move damage by 25% during eclipse.

SCHADENFREUDE.name: Schadenfreude
SCHADENFREUDE.description: Restores 1/4th health after any foe faints.

SCOUREDSILHOUETTE.name: Scoured Silhouette
SCOUREDSILHOUETTE.description: Upon entry during sandstorm, lowers foe's Attack and Sp. Atk by two steps.

SEALINGBODY.name: Sealing Body
SEALINGBODY.description: Moves used on the Pokémon are disabled for two turns.

SECRETIONSECRET.name: Secretion Secret
SECRETIONSECRET.description: When targeted by a status move, the offending Pokémon becomes poisoned.

SEEDSOWING.name: Seed Sowing
SEEDSOWING.description: Special moves have a 30% chance to leech targets.

SELECTIVESCUTES.name: Selective Scutes
SELECTIVESCUTES.description: Boosts one defending stat by two steps according to the foe's Attack and Sp. Atk.

SENTRY.name: Sentry
SENTRY.description: Takes 25% less damage while using a status move.

SERVEDCOLD.name: Served Cold
SERVEDCOLD.description: Boosts Attack by 20% in hail, or 40% if also below half health.

SEVERE.name: Severe
SEVERE.description: Its attacks are critical against numbed targets.

SHARPSHOOTER.name: Sharpshooter
SHARPSHOOTER.description: Doubles the critical hit chance of random crit moves. The Pokémon's Speed is doubled while using them.

SHELLCRACKER.name: Shellcracker
SHELLCRACKER.description: Its physical attacks reduce the target's Defense.

SHIFTINGFIST.name: Shifting Fist
SHIFTINGFIST.description: Punching moves change the Pokémon's secondary type and their power is boosted by 30%.

SHOCKWINGS.name: Shock Wings
SHOCKWINGS.description: Flying-type attacks have a 40% chance to numb.

SICKENING.name: Sickening
SICKENING.description: Special moves against it lower the attacker's Speed and Sp. Atk.

SIGNALJAM.name: Signal Jam
SIGNALJAM.description: The Pokémon and other battlers don't benefit from same-type attacking bonus.

SILVERLINING.name: Silver Lining
SILVERLINING.description: Boosts Speed by 50% in rainstorm. Doubles random added effect chance in rainstorm.

SILVERSENSE.name: Silver Sense
SILVERSENSE.description: Doubles critical hit chance. Restores HP for half the damage it does with critical hits.

SINKINGFEELING.name: Sinking Feeling
SINKINGFEELING.description: At the end of each round, lowers other waterlogged Pokémon's Attack and Sp. Atk by two steps.

SIPHONSNIPER.name: Siphon Sniper
SIPHONSNIPER.description: On the first turn, its attacks leech the target.

SIRENSONG.name: Siren Song
SIRENSONG.description: After using a sound move, lowers one of each foe's Attack and Sp. Atk, whichever is higher.

SLAPSTICK.name: Slapstick
SLAPSTICK.description: Whenever a foe fails or misses, they take 1/8th HP damage.

SLICKSURFACE.name: Slick Surface
SLICKSURFACE.description: Can't be leeched, drained, or trapped.

SLINKY.name: Slinky
SLINKY.description: Two-turn retreat moves such as Dig deal double damage.

SLIPSTREAM.name: Slipstream
SLIPSTREAM.description: Attack is boosted by 50% if a Tailwind is blowing.

SLUGGISH.name: Sluggish
SLUGGISH.description: The Pokémon is also Bug-type, but its Speed is halved.

SLUMBERINGDRAKE.name: Slumbering Drake
SLUMBERINGDRAKE.description: Falls asleep upon entry, but raises all of its stats by two steps.

SNOOZEFEST.name: Snoozefest
SNOOZEFEST.description: Whenever the Pokémon falls asleep, each other battler becomes drowsy.

SNOWSHROUD.name: Snow Shroud
SNOWSHROUD.description: The Pokémon takes 30% less move damage in hail.

SOLARCELL.name: Solar Cell
SOLARCELL.description: Boosts the Pokémon's Sp. Atk and Sp. Def by 30% in sunshine.

SOPPING.name: Sopping
SOPPING.description: Physical attacks against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to waterlog the attacker.

SOUNDBARRIER.name: Sound Barrier
SOUNDBARRIER.description: After using a sound move, raises the Pokémon's Defense and Sp. Def. Caps out at +4.

SPACEINTERLOPER.name: Space Interloper
SPACEINTERLOPER.description: Attacks hit twice for half damage, drain 25% of damage dealt and become special.

SPARESCALES.name: Spare Scales
SPARESCALES.description: Raises defenses after using a Grass-, Ground-, or Steel-type move. Caps out at +4.

SPECTRUMVISION.name: Spectrum Vision
SPECTRUMVISION.description: The Pokémon and its allies' moves are twice as likely to be critical.

SPINESPLODE.name: Spinesplode
SPINESPLODE.description: Leaves two layers of spikes after it self-destructs.

SPINTENSITY.name: Spintensity
SPINTENSITY.description: Speed is raised each turn. Speed is reset when hit, but the attacker takes 1/8th HP damage for each step lost.

STABILITY.name: Stability
STABILITY.description: Can't be afflicted with any non-volatile status condition.

STAGGERINGSLAPS.name: Staggering Slaps
STAGGERINGSLAPS.description: Has a 30% chance to dizzy targets when using physical moves.

STAINLESSSTEEL.name: Stainless Steel
STAINLESSSTEEL.description: Prevents stat steps from being lowered (except when self-inflicted). Immune to weather downsides.

STAMPEDE.name: Stampede
STAMPEDE.description: Doubles critical hit chance for each Speed step up. All moves can random critical hit.

STARGUARDIAN.name: Star Guardian
STARGUARDIAN.description: Sets a Light Screen for 4 turns upon entering the battle.

STARSALIGN.name: Stars Align
STARSALIGN.description: During eclipse, its moves can't miss and always activate their random effects.

STEAMPOWER.name: Steam Power
STEAMPOWER.description: Takes 50% less damage from Water-type moves. Raises Speed by four steps when hit by one.

STEELABSORB.name: Steel Absorb
STEELABSORB.description: Immune to Steel-type moves and restores 25% of max HP if hit by one.

STEEPFLYING.name: Steep Flying
STEEPFLYING.description: Fly and Dive Bomb deal 50% more damage.

STICKYFINGERS.name: Sticky Fingers
STICKYFINGERS.description: Can hold a second item by stealing it.

STICKYMOLD.name: Sticky Mold
STICKYMOLD.description: If an attack lowers its HP to half or less, leeches the attacker.

STONEMANE.name: Stone Mane
STONEMANE.description: Prevents half the self-damage from recoil. Powers up moves that have recoil damage by 20%.

STORMBRINGER.name: Stormbringer
STORMBRINGER.description: Summons rainstorm for four turns when hit by an attack.

STORMTOTEM.name: Storm Totem
STORMTOTEM.description: Upon entry, summons a Turbulent Sky on the Pokémon's side for 6 turns.

STRAIGHTAHEAD.name: Straight Ahead
STRAIGHTAHEAD.description: Ignores Abilities that would affect its moves. Its attacks can't be redirected to new targets.

STRESSFUL.name: Stressful
STRESSFUL.description: Makes foes stressed and unable to use their items.

STRIKETWICE.name: Strikes Twice
STRIKETWICE.description: In rainstorm, each of its hits is followed by an extra hit at 25% power.

STUBBORN.name: Stubborn
STUBBORN.description: Prevents its stats from being lowered by more than one step at a time.

STUPEFYING.name: Stupefying
STUPEFYING.description: Ignores Abilities that would affect its moves. Dizzies opponents that it hits below half health.

STYGIANNIGHT.name: Stygian Night
STYGIANNIGHT.description: Changes the weather to Blood Moon, which heralds the Full Blood Moon. Lingers for 3 turns after leaving.

STYLISH.name: Stylish
STYLISH.description: The Pokémon benefits twice as much from style points.

SUBSPACESCHISM.name: Subspace Schism
SUBSPACESCHISM.description: Upon entry, creates a Trick Room for four turns, inverting the effect of Speed.

SUDDENCHILL.name: Sudden Chill
SUDDENCHILL.description: Special moves against the Pokémon have a 30% chance to frostbite the attacker.

SUDDENTURN.name: Sudden Turn
SUDDENTURN.description: Uses Rapid Spin after its first attack to clear hazards, raise Speed, and deal damage.

SUMMITSPIRIT.name: Summit Spirit
SUMMITSPIRIT.description: Boosts Sp. Atk by 30% in hail.

SUNBURNING.name: Sun Burning
SUNBURNING.description: At the end of each turn in sunshine, each Pokémon not immune to sunshine has their Defense and Sp. Def lowered.

SUNCHASER.name: Sun Chaser
SUNCHASER.description: Boosts the Pokémon's Attack by 30% in sunshine.

SUNEATER.name: Sun Eater
SUNEATER.description: Summons eclipse for four turns when hit by an attack.

SURVIVALIST.name: Survivalist
SURVIVALIST.description: It avoids hazards and can't be knocked out with one hit.

SWIFTSTOMPS.name: Swift Stomps
SWIFTSTOMPS.description: The Pokémon's Speed is doubled while using kicking moves.

SWORDPLAY.name: Swordplay
SWORDPLAY.description: Boosts the power of blade moves by 30%.

TAIGATREKKER.name: Taiga Trekker
TAIGATREKKER.description: During hail, boosts Speed and Grass-type damage by 50%.

TANTALIZING.name: Tantalizing
TANTALIZING.description: Draws in attacks from enemies with below half health.

TEAMPLAYER.name: Team Player
TEAMPLAYER.description: Deals 25% more move damage for each ally in battle.

TENDERIZE.name: Tenderize
TENDERIZE.description: At the end of each round, lowers other numbed Pokémon's Defense and Sp. Def by two steps.

TERRITORIAL.name: Territorial
TERRITORIAL.description: Boosts damage by 20% if there is a weather. Immune to weather downsides.

TERRORIZE.name: Terrorize
TERRORIZE.description: Flinching moves always activate their random effects.

TESLACOILS.name: Tesla Coils
TESLACOILS.description: Becomes energy charged upon entry, doubling the power of its next Electric-type attack.

THIEFSDIVERSION.name: Thief's Diversion
THIEFSDIVERSION.description: By sacrificing a held item the Pokémon didn't start with, it can negate one attack against it.

THUNDERSTRUCK.name: Thunderstruck
THUNDERSTRUCK.description: Becomes energy charged when hit by an attack, doubling the power of its next Electric-type attack.

TIMEINTERLOPER.name: Time Interloper
TIMEINTERLOPER.description: Its attacks have priority, deal 25% less damage and become special.

TIMESKIP.name: Time Skip
TIMESKIP.description: Between each turn there's another turn where no one moves.

TOILANDTROUBLE.name: Toil and Trouble
TOILANDTROUBLE.description: Foes suffer 50% more move damage reduction from burn, frostbite, and numb.

TOLLTHEBELLS.name: Toll the Bells
TOLLTHEBELLS.description: Upon entry during eclipse, heals the lowest HP ally or self by 33%.

TORPORSAP.name: Torpor Sap
TORPORSAP.description: Restores its HP by 50% of the damage it deals to sleeping targets.

TOUGH.name: Tough
TOUGH.description: Takes half damage from Fighting- and Rock-type moves.

TOXICATTITUDE.name: Toxic Attitude
TOXICATTITUDE.description: Powers up Poison-type moves of itself and its allies by 50%.

TOXINTAX.name: Toxin Tax
TOXINTAX.description: Heals based on the damage other battlers take from being poisoned.

TRACTORBEAM.name: Tractor Beam
TRACTORBEAM.description: Prevents the foe from escaping during eclipse.

TRAPPER.name: Trapper
TRAPPER.description: Takes 30% less damage from Pokémon that are trapped.

TRAUMATIZING.name: Traumatizing
TRAUMATIZING.description: Foes whose stats are lowered by the Pokémon keep those lowered stats even after switching.

TRENCHCARVER.name: Trench Carver
TRENCHCARVER.description: The Pokémon's Speed is doubled while using recoil moves.

TUNEDOUT.name: Tuned Out
TUNEDOUT.description: Boosts the power of sound moves by 30%. Sound moves ignore the target's modified Defense and Sp. Def.

ULTRAADAPTED.name: Ultra Adapted
ULTRAADAPTED.description: Powers up moves of the same type by 50%.

UNAFRAID.name: Unafraid
UNAFRAID.description: Takes half damage from Dark- and Bug-type moves.

UNASSUMING.name: Unassuming
UNASSUMING.description: Before using a status move against a single foe, lowers their Defense by two steps.

UNBOUND.name: Unbound
UNBOUND.description: Moves ignore Abilities that would affect its moves or activate after hitting the target, and immunities due to typing.

UNBREAKABLE.name: Unbreakable
UNBREAKABLE.description: Prevents half the self-damage from recoil and Self-Destruct/Explosion.

UNCANNYLUCK.name: Uncanny Luck
UNCANNYLUCK.description: If an attacker would activate a random added effect on the Pokémon, that effect is placed on the attacker instead.

UNCONQUERABLE.name: Unconquerable
UNCONQUERABLE.description: Blocks random added effects of attacks taken, and prevents critical hits.

UNCONVENTIONAL.name: Unconventional
UNCONVENTIONAL.description: Moves that use stats other than the default deal 50% more damage.

UNFAZED.name: Unfazed
UNFAZED.description: Takes 20% less damage from neutrally effective attacks.

UNNERVE.name: Unnerve
UNNERVE.description: Makes the foe nervous and unable to eat Berries or Leftovers.

VANDAL.name: Vandal
VANDAL.description: Deals 30% more damage to targets that have an item. After attacking a foe, destroys their clothing items.

VENGEANCE.name: Vengeance
VENGEANCE.description: After an attack reduces its HP to half or less, deals 1/4 of the attacker's HP back to the attacker.

VENOMDETTA.name: Venomdetta
VENOMDETTA.description: Immune to Poison-type moves, and raises Attack and Sp. Atk if hit by one.

VENOMGORGER.name: Venom Gorger
VENOMGORGER.description: Whenever a foe's poison worsens, the Pokémon heals for 25% max HP.

VERDANT.name: Verdant
VERDANT.description: Powers up Grass-type moves of itself and its allies by 50%.

VICTORYMOLT.name: Victory Molt
VICTORYMOLT.description: Heals non-volatile status conditions and resets stat changes after knocking out any Pokémon.

VIGILANT.name: Vigilant
VIGILANT.description: Takes 40% less damage while using a status move.

VITALRHYTHM.name: Vital Rhythm
VITALRHYTHM.description: At the end of each turn, itself and each ally heals for 1/16th of their HP.

WALLNINJA.name: Wall Ninja
WALLNINJA.description: The Pokémon's attacks are always critical if there is an active Room.

WATERFALLCONDITIONING.name: Waterfall Conditioning
WATERFALLCONDITIONING.description: Boosts Speed by 50% in rainstorm. Can't miss during rainstorm.

WEATHERED.name: Weathered
WEATHERED.description: Immune to weather downsides, and takes 20% less damage from attacks during weather.

WELLSUITED.name: Well Suited
WELLSUITED.description: Takes 50% less damage from not-very-effective or barely-effective attacks.

WHITEKNIGHT.name: White Knight
WHITEKNIGHT.description: Draws in moves from foes with base power 100 or more. Takes 15% less move damage.

WIBBLEWOBBLE.name: Wibble Wobble
WIBBLEWOBBLE.description: Uses Power Split upon entry or when hit by a move.

WILDTOTEM.name: Wild Totem
WILDTOTEM.description: Upon entry, summons a Primal Forest on the Pokémon's side for 6 turns.

WILLAURA.name: Will Aura
WILLAURA.description: Upon entry, creates a Willful Room for four turns, reducing all hits by 30 damage.

WINTERINSULATION.name: Winter Insulation
WINTERINSULATION.description: During hail, immune to Fire- and Electric-type moves.

WINTERSWAGES.name: Winter's Wages
WINTERSWAGES.description: Restores HP based on damage taken by others from hail.

WIRECUTTER.name: Live Wire
WIRECUTTER.description: Lays an electrical hazard around the opponent when its HP is lowered below half.

WISEHUNTER.name: Wise Hunter
WISEHUNTER.description: After knocking out any Pokémon, raises its Sp. Atk and Sp. Def.

WISHMAKER.name: Wish Maker
WISHMAKER.description: The random added effects of moves by all battlers always activate.

WORLDQUAKE.name: Worldquake
WORLDQUAKE.description: Ground-type moves deal 50% more damage in eclipse.

WRATHINSTINCT.name: Wrath Instinct
WRATHINSTINCT.description: Uses Dragon Dance if an attack lowers its HP to half or below.

WREAKHAVOC.name: Wreak Havoc
WREAKHAVOC.description: Boosts the power of rampaging moves by 30%, and makes them physical or special based on which would be more effective.

AFTERYOU.name: After You
AFTERYOU.description: The user helps the target and makes it use its move right after the user.

ASSIST.name: Assist
ASSIST.description: The user hurriedly and randomly uses a move among those known by other Pokémon in the party.

BELLYDRUM.name: Belly Drum
BELLYDRUM.description: The user maximizes its Attack stat in exchange for HP equal to half its max HP.

BESTOW.name: Bestow
BESTOW.description: The user passes its held item to the target when the target isn't holding an item.

BIDE.name: Bide
BIDE.description: The user endures attacks for two turns, then strikes back to cause double the damage taken.

BLOCK.name: Block
BLOCK.description: The user blocks the target's way with arms spread wide to prevent escape.

BODYSLAM.name: Body Slam
BODYSLAM.description: The user drops onto the target with its full body weight. It has a 30% chance to numb.

BOOMBURST.name: Boomburst
BOOMBURST.description: The user attacks everything around it with the destructive power of a terrible, explosive sound.

CONVERSION.name: Conversion
CONVERSION.description: The user changes its type to become the same type as one of its moves.

CONVERSION2.name: Conversion 2
CONVERSION2.description: The user changes its type to make itself resistant to the type of the attack the opponent used last.

COVET.name: Covet
COVET.description: The user approaches the target, then steals their item. Items stolen from wild Pokémon are stored.

DIZZYPUNCH.name: Dizzy Punch
DIZZYPUNCH.description: The target is hit with rhythmically launched punches that have a 30% chance to dizzy.

DOUBLEEDGE.name: Double-Edge
DOUBLEEDGE.description: A reckless, life-risking tackle. The user also takes 33% recoil.

ECHOEDVOICE.name: Echoed Voice
ECHOEDVOICE.description: The user attacks the foe with an echoing voice. If this move is used every turn, it does greater damage.

ENCORE.name: Encore
ENCORE.description: The user compels the target to keep using only the move it last used for three turns.

ENDEAVOR.name: Endeavor
ENDEAVOR.description: An attack move that cuts down the target's HP to equal the user's HP.

ENDURE.name: Endure
ENDURE.description: The user endures any attack with at least 1 HP. It always fails if it is used in succession.

ENTRAINMENT.name: Entrainment
ENTRAINMENT.description: The user dances to compel the target to mimic it, making the target's Ability the same as the user's.

EXPLOSION.name: Explosion
